@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-10 rounded-xl leading-loose">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-700">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
        This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>ExpenseManager</strong> collects, uses, and protects your information
        when you use our application. By registering or using ExpenseManager, you agree to the practices described below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Registration Data:</strong> First name, last name, email address, and password.</li>
        <li><strong>Expense Data:</strong> Item name, amount, category, date, and description of expenses.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        We use the collected data to:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>Authenticate and manage user accounts.</li>
        <li>Allow you to record and track your expenses.</li>
        <li>Provide insights and reports about your spending.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        All data is private to the user. We do not share, sell, or rent your personal or expense data to any third
        parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        Your data is stored in a local database. Passwords are securely hashed, and sensitive information is
        encrypted. We take reasonable steps to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. User Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <li>You can delete your account at any time.</li>
        <li>You can request an export of your expense data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        ExpenseManager does not use third-party cookies or tracking tools. Only session cookies may be used for login
        and authentication purposes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        ExpenseManager is designed for students and individuals managing their finances. It is not intended for
        children under 13. If you are under 13, please do not use this application.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">8. Contact Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
    </p>
    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-700">
        📧 Email: <a href="mailto:supekaraniket34@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">supekaraniket34@gmail.com</a><br />
        🌐 GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/supekar-aniket" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">github.com/supekar-aniket</a>
    </p>

    
</div>

